Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:08.28,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Leaving aside goodbyes, let to carry a flower
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.49,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With uncertainty the dawn breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:16.00,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I woke up in a room alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:20.03,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With that warmth as the only thing left
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:43.40,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even though I don't remember a thing about last night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:50.38,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Someone else was there, and I am confirming that thought
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:59.03,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm still hungover, and can't think straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:05.92,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Although I don't understand anything, well, what can I do? That also is beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.60,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A toothbrush on the wash stand, someone's drinking cup, a face lotion on the shelf
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.39,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything is just things I have no memories about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.43,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The pillow smells of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.98,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Leaving aside goodbyes, let to carry a flower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:30.18,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With uncertainty the dawn breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:33.80,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I am waking up in a room alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:38.01,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With that warmth as the only thing left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:02:01.49,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even though I really don't remember last night that well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:08.80,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I suspect I've been a subject to a badger game, but it doesn't feel like it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:20.73,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Though I've been thinking about it with an already sober mind, it's fine if I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.12,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Or rather, thinking this way is fine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:31.99,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Lavender blooming by the window, dirty sink, a knitted muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.88,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything is just things I have no memories about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.85,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The room smells of spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:44.44,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A flower badger game akin to grasping for drifting clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.65,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}With nobody coming, the sun sets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.25,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Only the window tinged with setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:56.16,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Left me there knowing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:19.68,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I only remember a little of what actually happened last night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:26.31,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Living without you, and that that will continue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:35.21,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now I still only think about that one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:42.12,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}About you disappearing, giving me but a single flower
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:50.20,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You will surely return tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.18,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Returning with an expression as if nothing happened
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.33,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even now I hear the door opening
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.85,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Saying "Sorry, I'm late"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.94,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm always waiting for nothing but words
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:10.54,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Patiently waiting for the evening glow of a sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:22.63,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Before completely forgetting, picture the flowers in your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.91,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today as well, alone, the night comes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.47,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}By myself, I slumber in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:34.39,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Left with that warmth for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:38.40,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Foolishly, love is a given flower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.44,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even in this room spring will come again
